author: Brinton Parker
title: Steven Yeun and His Wife Are Positively Glowing With Baby Joy
text:
Steven Yeun and Joana Pak Pregnancy Instagram Steven Yeun and His Wife Are Positively Glowing With Baby Joy February 14, 2017 A post shared by Steven Yeun (@steveyeun) on Feb 13, 2017 at 7:46pm PST 
If you're looking for a little dose of happiness for your day, look no further than The Walking Dead star Steven Yeun's latest Instagram photo. Steven and his wife, Joana Pak, not only have the obvious giddiness of newlyweds , but they're also glowing with pregnancy joy ! The expectant parents used a photo booth as an opportunity to highlight Joana's rapidly growing baby bump, and their love is too sweet for words. 
Understandably, Steven's fans are overwhelmed with excitement for the couple and their growing family; some have even called out details, wondering whether Steven is dropping hints about Joana's pregnancy with his peace sign and double-bee caption. While we can't speak for any theories, we can say one thing with certainty: this couple is the absolute cutest. Congratulations, you two!
